{"title":"绿颂","authors":["张国忠"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":5,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张国忠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿染孟春，点大地之美；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿扮仲夏，庇人间之荫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿隐深秋，扶红花之艳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿缀严冬，显生命之本。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿的炫目、绿的透彻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如橄榄园枚枚苞放的奇葩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿的庄严、绿的神圣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如边防线尊尊永恒的雕像；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿的虔诚、绿的忠贞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿到晴云秋月，直乃挺身徇义；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿的温柔、绿的刚烈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿到殁而不朽，只留千古绝唱。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}